      </div>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon fire">üî•</div>
          <h3>Pellet-Powered Heat</h3>
          <p>Efficient, clean-burning wood pellets provide consistent, controllable heat for the perfect sauna experience.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon nature">üå≤</div>
          <h3>Sustainable Design</h3>
          <p>Crafted from natural materials with a focus on environmental responsibility and renewable fuel sources.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon precision">‚öôÔ∏è</div>
          <h3>Precision Engineering</h3>
          <p>Advanced temperature control and airflow management for optimal performance and safety.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon aesthetic">‚ú®</div>
          <h3>Timeless Aesthetic</h3>
          <p>Modern lines meet traditional craftsmanship in a stove that's as beautiful as it is functional.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section> -->

  <!-- Specifications -->
  <section class="specifications">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="spec-grid">
        <div class="spec-content">
          <h2>Technical Specifications</h2>
          <p class="spec-intro">Built to last, designed to perform</p>

          <div class="spec-list">
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Heating Capacity</span>
              <span class="spec-value">6-12 m¬≤ sauna</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Fuel Type</span>
              <span class="spec-value">Wood Pellets</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Material</span>
              <span class="spec-value">Steel & Cast Iron</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Weight</span>
              <span class="spec-value">45 kg</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Warranty</span>
              <span class="spec-value">5 Years</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Certification</span>
              <span class="spec-value">CE Certified</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="spec-visual">
          <div class="placeholder-box stove-detail">
            <span>Technical Drawing or Detail Shot</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-image">
          <div class="placeholder-box nature-scene">
            <span>Nature-inspired imagery</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2>Pellet Sauna<br/>Company</h2>
          <p class="lead">
            We believe that the best sauna experiences come from a harmony of tradition and innovation.
          </p>
          <p>
            The P1 represents our commitment to creating heating solutions that respect both the
            environment and the timeless ritual of the sauna. Every stove is engineered for performance,
            designed for beauty, and built to last generations.
          </p>
          <p>
            From the natural wood finishes to the precision-engineered combustion system, every detail
            reflects our dedication to quality and sustainability.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container-small">
      <div class="section-header centered">
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>Ready to transform your sauna experience?</p>
      </div>

      <form class="contact-form">
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Your Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Your Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="subject">Subject</label>
          <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" required></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Send Message</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-content">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <h3>Pellet Sauna<br/>Company</h3>
          <p>Sustainable warmth for the modern sauna</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <div class="footer-column">
            <h4>Product</h4>
            <a href="#product">P1 Stove</a>
            <a href="#features">Features</a>
            <a href="#specifications">Specs</a>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-column">
            <h4>Company</h4>
            <a href="#about">About Us</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2025 Pellet Sauna<br/>Company. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Navigation */
  .nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 1000;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light-gray);
  }

  .nav-container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .brand {
    font-family: 'Playwrite NO', cursive;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .nav-link {
    color: var(--text-medium);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .nav-link:hover {
    color: var(--stove-charcoal);
  }

  /* Hero Section */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--mist-light) 0%, var(--sky-light) 100%);
    padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 80vh;
  }

  .hero-text {
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 15vw, 12rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 0.9;
    color: var(--stove-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    color: var(--text-medium);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-medium);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 540px;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .stat {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--stove-dark);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-medium);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--stove-dark);
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--stove-charcoal);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--stove-dark);
    border: 2px solid var(--stove-dark);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--stove-dark);
    color: white;
  }

  /* Hero Image */
  .hero-image {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: visible;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .product-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: none;
    transform: scale(2.2) translateY(-10%);
    transform-origin: center center;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .product-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15));
  }

  /* Hide placeholder when image loads */
  .product-img:not([src=""]) ~ .product-placeholder {
    display: none;
  }

  .product-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--sky-medium) 0%, var(--wood-light) 100%);
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 2px dashed rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .placeholder-content {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .placeholder-icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .placeholder-content code {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  /* Floating Card */
  .floating-card {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 6rem;
    right: 4rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    max-width: 250px;
    z-index: 3;
  }

  .card-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--fire-glow);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .floating-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .floating-card p {
    color: var(--text-medium);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* Shared Container Styles */
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .container-small {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-header.centered {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-medium);
  }

  /* Product Highlight */
  .product-highlight {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .highlight-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .image-wrapper {
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .placeholder-box {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .placeholder-box.sauna-interior {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--wood-medium) 0%, var(--wood-warm) 100%);
  }

  .placeholder-box.stove-detail {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--sky-medium) 0%, var(--stove-dark) 100%);
  }

  .placeholder-box.nature-scene {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--wood-natural) 0%, var(--wood-warm) 100%);
  }

  .highlight-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .highlight-content > p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-medium);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .feature-list .icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .feature-list strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .feature-list p {
    color: var(--text-medium);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Features Section */
  .features {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--mist-light);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-icon.fire {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--fire-orange) 0%, var(--fire-glow) 100%);
  }

  .feature-icon.nature {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--wood-natural) 0%, var(--wood-medium) 100%);
  }

  .feature-icon.precision {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--sky-blue) 0%, var(--sky-medium) 100%);
  }

  .feature-icon.aesthetic {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-warm) 0%, var(--wood-warm) 100%);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--text-medium);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Specifications */
  .specifications {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .spec-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .spec-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .spec-intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-medium);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .spec-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .spec-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light-gray);
  }

  .spec-label {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-medium);
  }

  .spec-value {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  /* About Section */
  .about {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--off-white);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .about-content .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-medium);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  /* Contact Section */
  .contact {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--stove-dark);
    color: white;
  }

  .contact .section-header h2,
  .contact .section-header p {
    color: white;
  }

  .contact-form {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .form-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .form-group {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .form-group label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--mist);
  }

  .form-group input,
  .form-group textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.125rem;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    color: white;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Work Sans', sans-serif;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .form-group input::placeholder,
  .form-group textarea::placeholder {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  .form-group input:focus,
  .form-group textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent-warm);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .btn-submit {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1.125rem;
    background: white;
    color: var(--stove-dark);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-submit:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    background: var(--stove-charcoal);
    color: var(--mist);
    padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .footer-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .footer-brand h3 {
    font-family: 'Playwrite NO', cursive;
